title: Naked and Afraid Season 3
description:
Each week, a new pair of complete and total strangers - one man and one woman - will find themselves stranded in and, quite literally, exposed to some of the world's most extreme weather environments. Each duo will be left high and dry with no food, no water... and no clothes. They must survive on their own for a full 21 days .
